{"data":[{"name":"101:1","price":"1. Al-Qâri‘ah (the striking Hour i.e. the Day of Resurrection).","arabic":"ٱلۡقَارِعَةُ","category":["101 (Al-Qari'ah)","Al-Qari'ah","Surah Al-Qari'ah"],"ayahNumber":6158,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"101:2","price":" 2. What is the striking (Hour)?","arabic":"مَا ٱلۡقَارِعَةُ","category":["101 (Al-Qari'ah)","Al-Qari'ah","Surah Al-Qari'ah"],"ayahNumber":6159,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"101:3","price":" 3. And what will make you know what the striking (Hour) is?","arabic":"وَمَآ أَدۡرَىٰكَ مَا ٱلۡقَارِعَةُ","category":["101 (Al-Qari'ah)","Al-Qari'ah","Surah Al-Qari'ah"],"ayahNumber":6160,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"101:4","price":" 4. It is a Day whereon mankind will be like moths scattered about.","arabic":"يَوۡمَ يَكُونُ ٱلنَّاسُ كَٱلۡفَرَاشِ ٱلۡمَبۡثُوثِ","category":["101 (Al-Qari'ah)","Al-Qari'ah","Surah Al-Qari'ah"],"ayahNumber":6161,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"101:5","price":" 5. And the mountains will be like carded wool.","arabic":"وَتَكُونُ ٱلۡجِبَالُ كَٱلۡعِهۡنِ ٱلۡمَنفُوشِ","category":["101 (Al-Qari'ah)","Al-Qari'ah","Surah Al-Qari'ah"],"ayahNumber":6162,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"101:6","price":" 6. Then as for him whose balance (of good deeds) will be heavy,[1]","arabic":"فَأَمَّا مَن ثَقُلَتۡ مَوَٰزِينُهُۥ","category":["101 (Al-Qari'ah)","Al-Qari'ah","Surah Al-Qari'ah"],"ayahNumber":6163,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"(V.101:6) See footnote of (V.7:8).","lang":"en"},{"name":"101:7","price":" 7. He will live a pleasant life (in Paradise).","arabic":"فَهُوَ فِي عِيشَةٖ رَّاضِيَةٖ","category":["101 (Al-Qari'ah)","Al-Qari'ah","Surah Al-Qari'ah"],"ayahNumber":6164,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"101:8","price":" 8. But as for him whose balance (of good deeds) will be light,","arabic":"وَأَمَّا مَنۡ خَفَّتۡ مَوَٰزِينُهُۥ","category":["101 (Al-Qari'ah)","Al-Qari'ah","Surah Al-Qari'ah"],"ayahNumber":6165,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"101:9","price":" 9. He will have his home in Hâwiyah (pit, i.e. Hell).","arabic":"فَأُمُّهُۥ هَاوِيَةٞ","category":["101 (Al-Qari'ah)","Al-Qari'ah","Surah Al-Qari'ah"],"ayahNumber":6166,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"101:10","price":" 10. And what will make you know what it is?","arabic":"وَمَآ أَدۡرَىٰكَ مَا هِيَهۡ","category":["101 (Al-Qari'ah)","Al-Qari'ah","Surah Al-Qari'ah"],"ayahNumber":6167,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"101:11","price":" 11. (It is) a fiercely blazing Fire!","arabic":"نَارٌ حَامِيَةُۢ","category":["101 (Al-Qari'ah)","Al-Qari'ah","Surah Al-Qari'ah"],"ayahNumber":6168,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"}],"chapter":["101 (Al-Qari'ah)","Al-Qari'ah","Surah Al-Qari'ah","Chapter Al-Qari'ah","Qari'ah","Surah Qari'ah","Chapter Qari'ah","Al Qari'ah","Surah Al Qari'ah","Chapter Al Qari'ah","Surah 101","Chapter 101","The Calamity","القارعة"]}